725294f-a.title: Queens: 39th Avenue - 30th Street
725294f-a.text:
39th Avenue, north side, from 3Oth to 31st Streets.
View 1 is from near 31st Street; view 2 from 30th Street.
The center building, that looks like a church, is occupied
by F. Ane Company, Lnc., Millwrights and Machinists.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 1 June 3, 1927
View 2: March 23, 1932
